      <number>7</number>
      <description>Standard</description>
    </StandardHierarchyLevel>
    <StatementCodes>
      <StatementCode>CCSS.Math.Content.4.MD.A.3</StatementCode>
    </StatementCodes>
    <Statements>
      <Statement>Apply the area and perimeter formulas for rectangles in real world and mathematical problems. &lt;i&gt;For example, find the width of a rectangular room given the area of the flooring and the length, by viewing the area formula as a multiplication equation with an unknown factor&lt;/i&gt;.</Statement>
    </Statements>
